        "name": "statistical-significance",
        "description": "Use when reporting numerical results, A/B test outcomes, or comparative metrics.",
        "content": "## Statistical Significance Reporting\n\n**Required checks before asserting a difference:**\n- Report sample size (n) for each group.\n- Report the p-value or confidence interval.\n- State the effect size, not just statistical significance.\n- Flag when sample size is too small for meaningful conclusions."
      }
    ],
